            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-818AROGP-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-818AROGP-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">INSCRIBED TO THE HONOURABLE SERJEANT KITE&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-818AROGP-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-818AROGP-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-818AROGP-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-818AROGP-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-818AROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-818AROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-1" n="1">In your indignation what mercy appears,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-2" n="2">While Jonathan's threatened with loss of his ears;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-3" n="3">For who would not think it a much better choice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-4" n="4">By your knife to be mangled than racked with your voice.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-5" n="5">If truly you would be revenged on the parson,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-6" n="6">Command his attendance while you act your farce on,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-7" n="7">Instead of your maiming, your shooting, or banging,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-8" n="8">Bid Povey secure him while you are haranguing.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-9" n="9">Had this been your method to torture him, long since,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818AROGP-line-10" n="10">He had cut his own ears to be deaf to your nonsense.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
